data.description: Move-In Ready ! Spacious 2-Story/1-Owner Home with 6 Bedrooms and 3.5 Baths with a Full Finished Basement on a Large Level Lot in a Very Stable Community. Freshly Painted Interior includes New Flooring Thorough-Out. Main Level offers a Separate Formal Living Room, Separate Formal Dining Room, Open Kitchen with Stainless Steel Appliances, Kitchen Island, Eat-In-Kitchen, Ceramic Backsplash, Corian Countertops and Plenty of Cabinet Space with a View to the Family Room.  Upper Level offers an Oversized Owner's Suite with a Setting Room, Double Vanity, Separate Tub & Shower and Huge Walk-In Closet. 4 additional Bedrooms, an Upgraded Bathroom and Laundry Room are on the Upper Level as well. Lower Level offers a Full Finished Basement that's a perfect set-up for an In-Law/Teen Suite with Full Bath and Space for a Home Office, Rec Room, Exercise Room, Bar and Storage. Exterior features a New Roof, Recently Replaced HVAC Unit, an Extended Deck & Patio for Entertaining/Relaxing with Access to the Shed in the Lengthy Backyard. Very Active HOA with Pool & Playground. Great Location with Easy Access to South Fulton Parkway, I-85, I-285, Hartsfield-Jackson International Airport and All the Attractions of Atlanta. See this Home Today, before it's SOLD on Tomorrow...*** Ask about the $10,000 in Down Payment Assistance Money
